name: Laura UnBound Eyes
description:
Laura UnBound at my studio in Downtown LA in late 2010. 
Laura has the most perfect skin and long brown hair. Since she was a traveling model I never got to shoot her as much as I would have liked, but when I did, we got some amazing images. Frankly, I was surprised she shot with me:) This is my first dip into NFTs so I hope you like it and will consider adding it to your collection and coming back to see what else I have for you in the future.
